quran[11{c,v,t}:
40,67,"wohi to hai jis ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir nutfay se, phir khoon ke lothrayse, phir woh tumhe bachay ki shakal mein nkalta hai, phir tumhe berhata hai taakay tum apni poori taaqat ko poanch jao, phir aur berhata hai taakay tum burhapay ko pohncho aur tum mein se koi pehlay hi wapas bulaa liya jata hai yeh sab kuch is liye kya jata hai taakay tum apne muqarrar waqt taq poanch jao, aur is liye ke tum haqeeqat ko samjhoo"
40,68,"wohi hai zindagi dainay wala, aur wohi mout dainay wala hai woh jis baat ka bhi faisla karta hai, bas aik hukum deta hai ke woh ho jaye aur woh ho jati hai"
40,69,"tum ne dekha unn logon ko jo Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre karte hain, kahan se woh phira-ay ja rahay hain ?"
40,70,yeh log jo iss kitaab ko aur unn saari kitabon ko jutlatay hain jo hum ne apne Rasolo-n ke sath bhaije theen? anqareeb inhen maloom ho jaye ga
40,71,"jab taoq un ki gardnon mein hon ge, aur zanjeeren, jin se pakar kar"
40,72,woh kholtey hue pani ki taraf kheinchain jayen ge aur phir dozakh ki aag mein jhonk diye jayen ge
40,73,phir unn se poocha jaye ga ke ab kahan hain Allah ke siwa woh dosray khuda jin ko tum shareek karte thay ?
40,74,"woh jawab den ge"" khoye gay woh hum se, balkay hum is se pehlay kisi cheez ko nah pkarte thay"" iss terhan Allah kafiroon ka gumraah hona muhaqqiqkar day ga"
40,75,"unn se kaha jaye ga"" yeh tumhara injaam is liye howa hai ke tum zameen mein ghair haq par magan thay aur phir uss par itratay thay"
40,76,"ab jao, jahannum ke darwazon mein daakhil ho jao hamesha tum ko wahein rehna hai, bohat hi bura thikana hai mutakbrin ka """
40,77,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo, Allah ka wada brhq hai ab khuwa hum tumahray samnay hi inn ko unn buray nataij ka koi hissa dikha den jin se hum aِnhin dara rahay hain, ya ( uss se pehlay ) tumhe duniya se utha len, palat kar aana to aِnhin hamari hi taraf hai"
